### Create Beer
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v3/beer
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("auth-id")}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "beerName": "presidente",
    "beerStyle": "LAGER",
    "upc": "xx",
    "quantityOnHand": 5,
    "price": 27.16
}

